{
  "id": "XtV6NerjQnYPtXgz",
  "name": "Leverage Copilot \u2014 ask the backlog",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Leverage Copilot\n\nChat with the **live n8n backlog**. Vector search (issues + PRs) + ranking tables + **comment deep-dive**.\n\n**Auth:** Set `LEVERAGE_COPILOT_SECRET` env var and pass as `x-leverage-secret` header. Unset = open access (dev only).\n\n**Demo:**\n- Why is #14361 ranked first?\n- Deep dive #14361 \u2014 what are maintainers saying?\n- What MCP issues hurt most?\n- code_scout: McpTrigger",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "db25aac0-6121-4cdf-9efe-a977b4cc9c3e",
      "name": "About",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
